<p>
  Please log in with your <a href="https://www.qrz.com/">QRZ.com</a> username and password.
</p>

<% if @error %>
  <p class="error"><%== @error %></p>
<% end %>

<form action="/login" method="post">
  <% if params[:net] %>
    <input type="hidden" name="net" value="<%== url_escape(params[:net]) %>"/>
  <% end %>
  <input name="call_sign" placeholder="call sign"/><br>
  <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="password"/><br/>
  <input type="submit" value="Log in"/>
</form>

<p>
  This server does <strong>not</strong> store your password. We only use it briefly
  to obtain a QRZ session identifier to use for lookups of call signs and photos.
</p>

<p>
  We recommend you enable <em>Two Factor Authentication</em> at the top of
  your Account page on <a href="https://www.qrz.com/">QRZ.com</a> for added
  security. Read more
  <a href="https://forums.qrz.com/index.php?threads/qrz-security-update-2fa-and-verified-users.661895/">about 2FA here</a>.
</p>
